title: MOTIVATIONAL SPEECH #1: People's Opinions Aren't Real
itunes:title: MOTIVATIONAL SPEECH #1: People's Opinions Aren't Real
description:
Episode 381 - This is one of my favorite episodes that I have ever recorded. In this episode, I talk about the influence of other's opinions in our lives, how to get past them and how to live like a happy and carefree kid again.
